171 A.3d 1256 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. HIRAM A. CELESTINE, A/K/A LEROY JOHNSON, LEROY A. JOHNSON, ANDRE FOSTER, ANDRE JOHNSON, ANDRE JONES, DIAMOND SIMS, ANDRE JOYNER, HIRAM CELSTINE, HIREN CELESTINE, CURTIS L. BEATON AND ANDY JOHNSON, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-220 Sept.Term 2017

079405 October 20, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002803-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
